    "definedTerms" : [ ]
  }, {
    "paragraph" : "6(d)",
    "text" : "lifting or carrying loads of at least 20 kilograms for at least 1 000 hours\r\nwithin the 15 years before the clinical onset of rotator cuff syndrome",
